txt.en: 'Just as I expected. Ugrukhôr was planning an attack against us! I am glad that you were able to hinder his plans. Still we must be watchful, as he may plan to retaliate.'

Many foes await those who dare enter the fortress of Durthang, home to the Captain of the Pit.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Durthang: The Dark Spire to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
